  (str orderNo) (int 63)
  (str title) (str Repealed.)
  (str content) (str `[Amendment of Certain Enactments.]--Rep. by the Repealing and Amending Act, 1964
(52 of 1964), s. 2 and First Schedule (w.e.f. 15-7-1978).`)
  (str footnotes) (str )
